      "para_id": "Q001506.1",
      "line_range": "1",
      "translation": "(1) For Ninmarki , the kind woman , the firstborn child of Nanše , his lady , Gudea , ruler of Lagaš , built her wall of Guabbatur , and inside it he built her temple ."
    }
